snippet.title: Aster Tatariqus - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Find your destiny in love, friendship, or family in the newest tactical RPG from Studio FgG!
Scheduled for release in 2023, Aster Tatariqus is a high fantasy smartphone game with tactical battles and an immersive story!

#AsterTatariqus #TacticalRPG #MobileGaming

Subscribe to our channel and follow us to get the latest news and content!

Official Website: https://at.fg-games.co.jp/en/
Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/AsterTatariqus
